ats away. Harmony and meaning vanish. The world irks me again with its variegated void.





IN MEMORY OF L. I. SHIGAEV


LEONID IVANOVICH SHIGAEV is dead.… The suspension dots, customary in Russian obituaries, must represent the footprints of words that have departed on tiptoe, in reverent single file, leaving their tracks on the marble.… However, I would like to violate this sepulchral silence. Please allow me to … Just a few fragmentary, chaotic, basically uncalled-for … But no matter